title: David Cameron makes Back to the Future Day joke at PMQs, ruins it for us all
text: David Cameron made a reference to Back to the Future day during Prime Minister’s Questions and ruined it for everyone involved. In response to a question from Iain Stewart on nuclear deterrent, the Cameron said it was “absolutely right” that Britain maintain Trident and highlighted his disappointment over Jeremy Corbyn's involvement in the CND. The 7 things Back to the Future actually got right 7 show all
